{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were-- what the signals corps unit did, the signals intelligence unit did-- and we-- the-- the British Army won the war against Rommel in the-- in the desert by doing what we were trained to do.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They set up triangular units and they were able to establish positions, enemy positions, and-- and send enemy information or disinformation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's what they did in the desert.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They set up dummy units so that he thought that the-- the regular Army units were in that area and, well, they were in other positions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were able to-- it was an enormous success.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they tried to do it so that this is what we trained for.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But then they knew we were going to enter the-- the Japanese war, so they trained us in Japanese language.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were all packed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were ready to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they dropped the bomb, and we never got to Japan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that was my Army experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went back to Forest Hills and lived with my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then I started to go to Pratt and worked in an art studio.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The news.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did the news reach you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my-- my uncle, who lived next door, as I had said before, he was sort of the paterfamilias and he arranged for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things and did all these things that had to be done.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got that information.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He must have written to him, because he had contacts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was very active in the Jewish community in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was active, had a lot of connections.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he-- I don't think my mother-- my mother was helping him too.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
